Name: Select - reduces an array to elements which fulfill a criterion

Synopsis:

array proc Select -> array 
Examples:[4 -2 0.3 -1.7 -3 0 7] {0 lt} Select -> [-2 -1.7 -3] 
[4 -2 0.3 -1.7 -3 0 7] {0 gt} Select -> [ 4  0.3  7]


